{{> head}}
{{> header}}

<main class="container py-4">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-text">
      <h1>About Y&amp;M Studios</h1>
      <p>
        Y&amp;M Studios offers a welcoming space for practitioners of all levels
        of fitness and ability. Our experienced instructors guide students through
        a range of yoga styles and mindfulness practices, from gentle beginner
        classes to more advanced workshops.
      </p>
      <p>
        We run around five sets of weekly classes at any given time, as well as
        weekend workshops once or twice a year. Whether you are completely new to
        yoga or looking to deepen an existing practice, there is a course for you.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-hero-image">
      <img src="/static/images/image3.jpg" alt="Yoga practitioner in a peaceful studio setting" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Our Classes</h2>
    <p>We offer two types of course:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Weekly blocks</strong> — a series of weekly sessions running
        across a number of weeks, ideal for building a consistent practice.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Weekend workshops</strong> — intensive courses held over two
        days, typically consisting of five sessions.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>Courses are available at beginner, intermediate, and advanced levels.</p>
    <p><a class="btn primary" href="/courses">View current and upcoming courses</a></p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Location</h2>
    <div class="location-box">
      <address>
        Y&amp;M Studios<br>
        12 Calm Street<br>
        Glasgow<br>
        G1 1YG
      </address>
      <p>We are located in the city centre, a short walk from Queen Street station.
      Accessible entrance on Calm Street. Free parking available on evenings and weekends.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

{{> footer}}